Params: Oh? Looks like there's a party in the Gray Raven lounge!
Let Nanami see what the Gray Ravens are up to!
...The Gray Raven Commandant sitting in the middle, wearing a strange headgear, with Liv whispering something beside. Lee and Kamui are arguing heatedly over something.
What they have in common is that they are all holding their controllers hard in their hands.
Nanami's hand sneakily plants her hand on the terminal of the lounge.
(How can they leave Nanami out of such FUN!)
(Aaaand... Done! Next, time for Nanami's showtime!)
(Ah! Then I might as well... And get everyone together to...)
(Oh? What's this? Let's have a lookie...)
You take off the device and see the suspicious Nanami doing her suspicious things to the terminal.
Those strange questions just now, those were Nanami's doing...
Nanami wanted to ask some interesting questions, but you just wouldn't answer them!
But whatever! Nanami is going to keep playing!
Nanami saw a watermelon on the beach just now!
And from the old files, humans always do this on the beach—they smash watermelons blindfolded!
But Nanami never understood the point of this... Maybe I'll understand if I get to experience it!
Commandant! Liv! Why did you two suddenly exit the game? Weird things are popping up on the beach! Hurry back!
We're coming now! Lee! You're still in the game, right?
Um, I don't have time to explain now... But we can't let Nanami break the watermelon! That watermelon is...
What... What are you talking about?
The watermelon is the reward for the beach volleyball earlier, and a very important mission item.
Really? It's my first time hearing about it...
What happens if the watermelon's smashed?
A "tragedy that can't be undone" will happen, and we'll fail the mission.
So we can't let Nanami destroy the mission target.
I'll be counting on you, Lee!
Right now, Lee stands alone on the beach.
So while the commandant and the others are trying to reconnect to the game, Lee will have to protect the mission item.
Lee nods. He rushes over with a serious look, the same as ever.
——Donning the armor that is a swimsuit, Lee enters a duel on the battlefield that is the beach.
